      <title>投资银行家说，不确定性危及S.非洲交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/investment-banker-says-uncertainty-imperils-south-africa-s-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府内部的断裂；以及全球宏观经济的不确定性＆mdash;根据该国最高投资银行家之一的说法，该国最大经济体的交易活动正在权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/investment-banker-says-uncertainty-imperils-south-africa-s-deals</guid>
