    <item>
      <title>中国股票在美国关税刺激刺激赌注时遭受适度的损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-slide-as-us-imposes-new-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票以创纪录的关税加息袭击美国几乎所有产品后，中国股票的中等下降，这是由于押注北京将采取更多措施掩盖经济的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-slide-as-us-imposes-new-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 01:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普关税威胁经济增长时，欧洲的股票下沉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布了一个世纪以来对贸易伙伴的最陡峭的美国关税之后，欧洲股票跌倒，其中包括欧盟的20％税率，欧盟正在考虑如何进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/european-stock-futures-decline-as-trump-tariffs-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股票下沉，随着贸易商的削减风险：市场包裹的债券，债券上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）竞标重制世界贸易秩序之后，全球金融市场遭到了彻底的抛售，这比预期的要比预期的要积极进取。]]></description>
